---
// Services Section - Tailwind grid + CSS personalizado inline
---

<section id="servicios" class="py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 xl:py-28 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Logo watermark -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03] z-0">
    <img src="/logo/logo2.svg" alt="" class="w-[450px] h-[450px] md:w-[600px] md:h-[600px] object-contain" />
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 xl:px-12 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Header de sección - Tailwind text utilities -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 md:mb-16 lg:mb-20 animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: 0.02em;" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-normal text-primary mb-4 md:mb-5 lg:mb-6 leading-none uppercase">
        Nuestros Servicios
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-secondary/80 leading-relaxed font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Soluciones integrales para el mantenimiento y reparación de sopladores industriales. 
        Servicio profesional en sitio para mantener su operación funcionando sin interrupciones.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Grid de servicios - Tailwind responsive grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-10">
      
      <!-- Servicio 1: Reparación -->
      <div class="services-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="services-icon">
          <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="services-title">
          Reparación de Sopladores
        </h3>
        
        <p class="services-description">
          Diagnóstico y reparación integral de sopladores industriales de todas las marcas y modelos. 
          Identificamos y solucionamos fallas mecánicas, eléctricas y de rendimiento.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="services-features">
          <li>Diagnóstico preciso de fallas</li>
          <li>Reparación de componentes mecánicos</li>
          <li>Corrección de problemas eléctricos</li>
          <li>Pruebas de funcionamiento</li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="/contacto" class="services-link">
          Solicitar servicio
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Servicio 2: Mantenimiento Preventivo -->
      <div class="services-card animate-on-scroll delay-200">
        <div class="services-icon">
          <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="services-title">
          Mantenimiento Preventivo
        </h3>
        
        <p class="services-description">
          Planes de mantenimiento programado diseñados para evitar paradas no planificadas. 
          Inspecciones periódicas y ajustes preventivos para maximizar la vida útil de sus equipos.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="services-features">
          <li>Inspecciones periódicas programadas</li>
          <li>Lubricación y ajustes</li>
          <li>Reemplazo de componentes de desgaste</li>
          <li>Reportes detallados de estado</li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="/contacto" class="services-link">
          Solicitar servicio
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Servicio 3: Mantenimiento Correctivo -->
      <div class="services-card animate-on-scroll delay-400">
        <div class="services-icon">
          <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="services-title">
          Mantenimiento Correctivo
        </h3>
        
        <p class="services-description">
          Intervención rápida ante fallas inesperadas para minimizar tiempos de inactividad. 
          Servicio de emergencia disponible para restablecer su operación lo antes posible.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="services-features">
          <li>Respuesta rápida ante emergencias</li>
          <li>Técnicos especializados en sitio</li>
          <li>Solución inmediata de fallas</li>
          <li>Minimización de tiempos muertos</li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="/contacto" class="services-link">
          Solicitar servicio
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- CTA adicional - Tailwind utilities -->
    <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 lg:mt-20 text-center animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-bg-cream to-bg-sand rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: 0.02em;" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-normal text-primary mb-4 md:mb-5 leading-none uppercase">
          ¿Necesita un servicio personalizado?
        </h3>
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-secondary/90 mb-6 md:mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
          Contacte con nuestro equipo técnico para evaluar sus necesidades específicas 
          y diseñar una solución a medida para su operación.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/contacto" 
          class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-rust to-primary text-white font-semibold px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 text-sm md:text-base"
        >
          Solicitar Cotización
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* ============================================
   SERVICES SECTION - Cards con efectos personalizados
   ============================================ */

.services-card {
  background: var(--color-white);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.8rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  height: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .services-card {
    padding: 2.25rem;
  }
}

/* Borde animado */
.services-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-rust), var(--color-steel));
  -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
  -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
  mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
  mask-composite: exclude;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
}

.services-card:hover::before {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Hover effect - elevación y sombra con nuevos colores */
.services-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  box-shadow: 
    0 10px 30px rgba(30, 49, 63, 0.18),
    0 4px 12px rgba(34, 53, 70, 0.12);
  border-color: transparent;
}

/* Ícono del servicio */
.services-icon {
  width: 56px;
  height: 56px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 1.25rem auto;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-steel));
  position: relative;
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .services-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }
}

.services-icon::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: -4px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-rust), var(--color-primary));
  z-index: -1;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
}

.services-card:hover .services-icon {
  transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
}

.services-card:hover .services-icon::after {
  opacity: 0.3;
}

.services-icon svg {
  width: 30px;
  height: 30px;
  color: var(--color-white);
  transition: transform 0.4s ease;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .services-icon svg {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
  }
}

.services-card:hover .services-icon svg {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}

/* Título del servicio */
.services-title {
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
  line-height: 1.4;
  text-align: center;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .services-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .services-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .services-title {
    font-size: 1.42rem;
  }
}

.services-card:hover .services-title {
  color: var(--color-rust);
}

/* Descripción */
.services-description {
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  font-size: 1rem;
  flex-grow: 1;
  text-align: center;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .services-description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .services-description {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
}

/* Lista de características */
.services-features {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
}

.services-features li {
  padding: 0.35rem 0;
  padding-left: 1.4rem;
  position: relative;
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.services-features li::before {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--color-rust);
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.services-card:hover .services-features li::before {
  transform: scale(1.2);
}

/* Botón "Más información" */
.services-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-top: 0.65rem;
  padding: 0.35rem 0;
  position: relative;
  transition: gap 0.3s ease;
  font-size: 0.93rem;
}

.services-link::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-rust), var(--color-primary));
  transition: width 0.3s ease;
}

.services-link:hover {
  gap: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-rust);
}

.services-link:hover::after {
  width: 100%;
}

.services-link svg {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.services-link:hover svg {
  transform: translateX(4px);
}

/* Efecto de brillo al pasar el mouse */
.services-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: -100%;
  width: 50%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    transparent,
    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
    transparent
  );
  transition: left 0.6s ease;
}

.services-card:hover::after {
  left: 100%;
}

/* Responsive - stacking en mobile */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .services-card {
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .services-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
  }
  
  .services-icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
  }
  
  .services-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
}
</style>
